item.title: 5150501 Ft. Dan Boeckner
item.description: Dan Boeckner (podcaster and front-man of Wolf Parade et al) joins us to talk about news, this time with heavy emphasis on Canadian and Israeli politics, plus the unfortunate shooting that happened at the SLC 50501/No Kings protest.GoFundMe for Afa Ah Loo:https://www.gofundme.com/f/urgent-support-needed-support-the-family-of-afa-ah-looFollow Dan: https://www.patreon.com/BOECKNERhttps://linktr.ee/Boeck9 Feed: https://feed.podbean.com/WesternKabuki/feed.xml
